trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.Executed> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewExecuted> routed events.
<xref:System.Windows.Input.ExecutedRoutedEventHandler> represents the method that implements the command logic of a <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Input.ExecutedRoutedEventHandler>表示实现一种<xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>。</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>命令逻辑的方法</xref:System.Windows.Input.ExecutedRoutedEventHandler>

trans-unit.source: Separating the implementation logic from the command allows the command to be invoked from different sources and types and enables the centralization of command logic.
trans-unit.target: 将实施逻辑分离命令中允许的命令从不同源和类型调用，并且允许的命令逻辑集中。

trans-unit.source: This event data class is also used for <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.Executed?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewExecuted?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 此事件数据类也会<xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.Executed?displayProperty=fullName>和<xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewExecuted?displayProperty=fullName>。</xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewExecuted?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.Executed?displayProperty=fullName>的使用

trans-unit.source: But most practical handlers will handle the <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding.Executed> events from a particular <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>, rather than work at the <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager> level.
trans-unit.target: 但大多数实际的处理程序将处理<xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding.Executed>从特定的事件<xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>，而不是在工作<xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager>级别。</xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager> </xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding> </xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding.Executed>

trans-unit.source: For more information on commanding, see [Commanding Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关命令的详细信息，请参阅[命令概述](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: Gets the command that was invoked.
The command associated with the event can be cast to the specific implementation of <xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>, if the type is known.
trans-unit.target: 与事件相关联的命令可以强制转换为的特定实现<xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>，如<xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>，如果类型未知。</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>

trans-unit.source: The command associated with this event.
Gets data parameter of the command.
trans-unit.target: 获取数据的命令的参数。

trans-unit.source: This property represents a generic data parameter that is defined by the particular command.
trans-unit.target: 此属性表示由特定命令的一般数据参数。

trans-unit.source: If this parameter is not needed, `null` can be passed.
trans-unit.target: 如果不需要此参数，`null`可以传递。

trans-unit.source: Normally, the Parameter is used to pass specific information to the command when it is executed.
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，参数用于执行时，将特定的信息传递给命令。

trans-unit.source: The type of the data is defined by the command.
trans-unit.target: 由该命令定义的数据类型。

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 默认值是<xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>。
